# See docs: https://docs.docker.com/build/concepts/context/#dockerignore-files
# The Docker Compose' build-context is "the repository root", because we want to access the shared "packages" folder inside each service.
# So we exclude all the files that are not needed for building the image, to speed up the build process.

.git
.env*
.dockerignore
